Created by Justice Action Media https://vimeo.com/justiceactionmedia and Maverick Media: https://maverickmedia.wordpress.com/ ORIGINAL: https://vimeo.com/14677394

Award-winning independent investigative journalist, author, and co-founder of Consortioumnews.com, Robert Parry, discusses the stunning rise to power of the "Neo-Cons," their influence on media, foreign policy, and our elected officials. Robert Gates, Afghanistan and elections also topic of interest.

For more related content, please visit: https://archive.org/details/@altviewstv-fanclub
